<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>Dear <%= first_and_last_name %>,</p>

    <p>VA received your application for the Rogers STEM scholarship on <%= application_date %>.</p>

    <p>We usually process applications within 30 days. We may contact you if we need more information or documents.</p>

    <p>
      <b>Rogers STEM Scholarship (Form 22-10203)</b>
      <br>
      for <%= first_and_last_name %>
      <br>
      Confirmation number <%= @claim.education_benefits_claim.confirmation_number %>
      <br>
      Date received <%= application_date %>
    </p>

    <p>
      <b>Your claim was sent to:</b>
      <br />
      Eastern Region
      <br />
      VA Regional Office
      <br />
      <%= EducationForm::EducationFacility::ADDRESSES[:eastern][0] %>
      <br />
      <%= EducationForm::EducationFacility::ADDRESSES[:eastern][1] %>
    </p>

    <p>
      <b>What happens after I apply?</b>
      <br />
      We usually decide on applications within 30 days.
      <br />
      You’ll get a Certificate of Eligibility (COE), or decision letter, in the mail.  If we’ve approved your application, you can bring this to the VA certifying official at your school.
      <br />
      <a href="https://www.va.gov/education/after-you-apply/">More about what happens after you apply</a>
    </p>

  </body>
</html>
